---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-950 w-full rounded-t-[2rem]">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
		<div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
				<img src="/favicon.ico" alt="Maya" class="h-7 w-7 rounded-md bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-950/90" />
				<span class="font-headline font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">Maya</span>
			</div>
			<p class="font-body text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
				Optimizando el flujo comercial del hub de las Américas con tecnología de vanguardia.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h4 class="font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">Soluciones</h4>
			<ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-sm">
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors" href="/#beneficios">Soluciones para operadores logísticos</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors" href="/#beneficios">App para transportistas en ruta</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors" href="/#beneficios">Seguimiento para destinatarios</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h4 class="font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">Recursos</h4>
			<ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-sm">
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors" href="/#analitica">Analítica y reportes en tiempo real</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors" href="/#faq">FAQ</a></li>
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors" href="/#formulario">Solicitar demostración</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h4 class="font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-50">Legal</h4>
			<ul class="space-y-4 font-body text-sm">
				<li><a class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 dark:hover:text-slate-50 transition-colors" href="/terminos">Términos</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 pb-12">
		<div class="pt-8 border-t border-outline-variant/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
			<p class="font-body text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">© {currentYear} Maya. CreiDev Solutions.</p>
			<p class="font-body text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
